Package com.ikueb.wallclock

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AlarmClockListener
    Specifies a listener on AlarmFixedWallClock.
    AlarmFixedWallClock
    Specifies a form of clock that can set alarms.
    FixedWallClock
    Specifies a form of clock that allows dates and times to be set.
    WallClock
    Specifies a form of clock that provides zoned and non-zoned dates and times.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractFixedWallClock
    A mutable WallClock abstract class that provides a fixed instant.
    FixedAlarmClock
    A mutable WallClock implementation that provides a fixed instant.
    FixedClock
    A mutable WallClock implementation that provides a fixed instant.
    TickingClock
    An immutable, ticking WallClock implementation that also extends from Clock.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TickingClock.UTCTickingClock
    An enum-driven singleton instance for a UTC-based TickingClock.
